window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Skharr wants a break. He needs a break in his life, and a quiet trip back to Verenvan. It doesn't look like that is going to happen.</p> <p>An old god might be making waves in a dungeon that has laid undisturbed for centuries. No one wants that to happen, so Skharr is asked by a local temple of Theros to get involved.</p> <p>Unfortunately, the temple does not have many resources to offer him. The one paladin who happens to be nearby is on a sabbatical. And she has definitely heard of the Barbarian of Theros.</p> <p>It's Skharr, a paladin on sabbatical, and three mercenaries who are just along for the treasure against what most likely will be power beyond a DeathEater's ability to handle.</p> <p>Not one to shy away from danger, Skharr and Horse aim their path back to Verenvar.</p> <p>They just need to find and kill an old god...and not die before they get there.</p>"; 
